OOC: Since no one knows what happened to him he got blown out of the way by 
some explosion in the battle at the Arc.

::Whistler::
    He woke up wondering what truck hit him, when he realized it was some 
annoying flying horse guy.  The next thing he wonders is how long he was out. 
 He slowly stands up and staggers over to the Arc to see what's going on.  
Halfway there he collapses on the ground in near agony.  In desperate hope he 
screams "HELP ME.  ANYONE"
